query:
INSERT INTO checklistItemResults (taskChecklistId, templateItemId, result, comments, photoUrls, createdAt)
SELECT 
  2 as taskChecklistId,
  cti.id as templateItemId,
  'na' as result,
  '' as comments,
  NULL as photoUrls,
  NOW() as createdAt
FROM checklistTemplateItems cti
WHERE cti.templateId = (
  SELECT templateId FROM taskChecklists WHERE id = 2
)
AND NOT EXISTS (
  SELECT 1 FROM checklistItemResults 
  WHERE taskChecklistId = 2 AND templateItemId = cti.id
)
